collectible.name: VoxCon VIP Lounge Designer Towel with Voxels Logo
collectible.description: First airdropped to those who signed the Guestbook at VoxCon's VIP Lounge. You can keep the towel as-is to hang it over voxel blocks, stretch it less-wide to hang it over a thin railing, or cover yourself in new and interesting ways. You will certainly need this after those purple jacuzzis in the VIP area though. Dry off the Cryptovoxels and welcome to Voxels, my friend! Limited edition of 300.
